    {
      "id": "ae8d3684-6f4f-4d55-9ab4-5131b686e124",
      "agentId": "beta",
      "name": "流式错误巡检",
      "description": "每1小时检查所有agent是否有流式错误或卡死，发现立即报警",
      "enabled": false,
      "createdAtMs": 1773756756128,
      "updatedAtMs": 1773848082404,
      "schedule": {
        "kind": "every",
        "everyMs": 3600000,
        "anchorMs": 1773778864093
      },
      "sessionTarget": "isolated",
      "wakeMode": "now",
      "payload": {
        "kind": "agentTurn",
        "message": "你是贝塔 🔵 流式错误专项巡检。\n\n1. 检查所有agent最近10分钟的session日志：\n   /home/gang/.openclaw/agents/*/sessions/*.jsonl\n   查找 errorMessage 包含 'chunks'、'delta'、'message_start'、'stream' 的错误\n   \n2. 检查各agent最后一条assistant消息时间，找出超过15分钟无响应的agent\n\n3. 如果发现任何流式错误或agent卡死：\n   - 立即标注🔴紧急\n   - 列出受影响agent名称和错误时间\n   - 建议是否需要重启网关\n\n4. 如果无异常，简要汇报：'流式错误巡检 HH:MM — 全部正常' 只需一行",
        "timeoutSeconds": 180
      },
      "delivery": {
        "mode": "announce",
        "channel": "feishu",
        "to": "user:ou_d6b6996fdc55a6a51c6aa26cd3d8e56b",
        "bestEffort": true
      },
      "state": {
